import sys
t = int(input())
while t != 0:
    (a, b, c, d, e) = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())
    f = a // c
    g = b // d
    h = min(f, g)
    if h >= e:
        print('YES')
        t -= 1
    else:
        print('NO')
        t -= 1

T = int(input())
for _ in range(T):
    (x, y, xr, yr, D) = map(int, input().split())
    print('YES') if min(x / xr, y / yr) >= D else print('NO')
